      <title>据称汉莎航空将在 IPO 前考虑投资波罗的海航空</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/lufthansa-said-to-consider-investment-in-air-baltic-before-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，德国汉莎航空集团正考虑在拉脱维亚国有航空公司波罗的海航空 (AirBaltic Corp.) 拟议的首次公开募股 (IPO) 之前收购该公司的股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/lufthansa-said-to-consider-investment-in-air-baltic-before-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 08:18:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
